# ğŸ“½ï¸ YouTube Transcript Summarizer with Gemini AI

**Day 3 â€“ AI Project**

## ğŸ“Œ Overview

This project automatically **fetches**, **cleans**, and **summarizes** the transcript of any YouTube video using:

* [`youtube-transcript-api`](https://pypi.org/project/youtube-transcript-api/) to get video transcripts
* **Google Gemini 2.5 Pro** for AI-powered summarization

You simply provide a YouTube link, and the script will:

1. Extract the video ID.
2. Fetch the transcript (if available).
3. Clean unwanted symbols, timestamps, and notes.
4. Summarize the content into **concise bullet points**.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

* âœ… **Automatic Video ID Extraction** from any YouTube link
* âœ… **Transcript Fetching** (if enabled for the video)
* âœ… **Text Cleaning** (removes timestamps, notes, and music symbols)
* âœ… **AI Summarization** using Google Gemini 2.5 Pro
* âœ… **Clear Output** in console with both transcript preview and summary

