---

## âš™ï¸ Configuration

In `main.py`, replace:

```python
GEMINI_API_KEY = "YOUR_API_KEY_HERE"
```

with your actual API key.

Also set your YouTube URL:

```python
YOUTUBE_URL = "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YOUR_VIDEO_ID"
```

